{"tid":443422,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Play推出App試用功能　即玩免下載","createTime":"2017-10-21T14:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T14:38:41.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d989f1c8a31068b2ab6a5412a3898c3458080b4f","tid":443422,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1925000/1929179/instantapp_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1925000%2F1929179%2Finstantapp_1024.png&h=f0f647f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle Play暫時得6個Apps可以試用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。（網站截圖）</div><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play上有近300萬個App，簡介質素參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用家下載後不時發現名不符實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Google Play去年已預告正研發App試用功能「Instant App」，據Techcrunch報道，該功能終於開通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n以往用家只能在下載App後才能了解該app的完整功能，新開設的「立即試用」按鈕，就可讓用戶免去下載的步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，先試用App<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n用戶可在手機瀏覽此網址，列出提供試用功能的Apps名單。暫時有6個Apps有此功能，包括《紐約時報》旗下的填字遊戲App、媒體App Buzzfeed、旅遊訂購App Skyscanner等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/collection/promotion_3002d0f_instantapps_featuredapps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fcollection%2Fpromotion_3002d0f_instantapps_featuredapps&d=G5okL0FRdGxf9J%2FhKIH%2FPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7d0b85d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/collection/promotion_3002d0f_instantapps_featuredapps</a><br />\n<br />\nTOPick編輯有試用過部分的App，因應載入介面需時，所需時間或與下載差不多，但免去下載App的數據流量及減少內存損耗仍是好消息，相信日後更多App增設試用功能後，對用戶會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle指出，現時Google Play每月新App下載數已超過80億次，每月活躍用戶達10億人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1929179/Google%20Play%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAApp%E8%A9%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%80%E5%8D%B3%E7%8E%A9%E5%85%8D%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1929179%2FGoogle%2520Play%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BAApp%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258D%25B3%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%2585%258D%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589&d=G5okL0FRdGxf9J%2FhKIH%2FPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=082a27b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1929179/Google%20Play%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAApp%E8%A9%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%80%E5%8D%B3%E7%8E%A9%E5%85%8D%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89</a>"}]}